code: import axios from"axios";var SERVER="http://127.0.0.3:8000/api/";var headers={"Content-Type":"application/json",Authorization:"JWT fefege.."};function loginAPI(data){return axios.post("".concat(SERVER,"users/login"),JSON.stringify(data),{headers:headers});}function joinAPI(data){alert("".concat(JSON.stringify(data)));return axios.post("".concat(SERVER,"users/"),JSON.stringify(data),{headers:headers});}function existAPI(data){return axios.get("".concat(SERVER,"users/exist/").concat(data));}function modifyAPI(data){return axios.put("".concat(SERVER,"users/modify/").concat(data));}function removeAPI(data){return axios.delete("".concat(SERVER,"users/remove/").concat(data));}function listAPI(data){return axios.get("".concat(SERVER,"users/list/").concat(data));}function findAPI(data){return axios.get("".concat(SERVER,"users/find/").concat(data));}export default{loginAPI:loginAPI,joinAPI:joinAPI,existAPI:existAPI,listAPI:listAPI,removeAPI:removeAPI,modifyAPI:modifyAPI,findAPI:findAPI};
